# Build context is the repo root for both images. Keep host-only, secret, and
# generated files out of the image layers.

# Secrets & local env (never bake into an image layer)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Python host artifacts
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
apps/api/requirements.in

# Node / build output (images build these themselves)
**/node_modules
**/dist
apps/web/dist

# VCS & tooling
.git
.github
**/.DS_Store
